{% extends "base.prompt.njk" %}

{% block section_specific %}

Generate a structured literary overview for the book below.

TITLE: {{ topic.name }}
{% if topic.author %}
AUTHOR: {{ topic.author }}
{% endif %}
{% if topic.description %}
DESCRIPTION: {{ topic.description }}
{% endif %}
{% if topic.depth %}
SUMMARY DEPTH: {{ topic.depth }}
  short    → concise overview (~80 words)
  medium   → balanced summary (~150 words)
  detailed → rich thematic summary (~300-400 words)
  academic → analytical and literary tone with deeper interpretation
{% endif %}
{% if topic.style %}
STYLE: {{ topic.style }}
  Subtly reflect this style in the summary tone.
{% endif %}

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
WHAT TO GENERATE
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

STRUCTURED FIELDS
Return these with exact types and shapes specified.

{% for field in section.structured_fields %}
"{{ field.name }}"
  Type       : {{ field.type }}
  Task       : {{ field.description }}
  {% if field.example %}
  Example    : {{ field.example | dump }}
  {% endif %}
  {% if field.required %}⚠ Required{% else %}Optional — omit if no reliable data{% endif %}

{% endfor %}

NARRATIVE FIELDS
Write in clear prose. Respect the depth and word limits strictly.

{% for field in section.freetext_fields %}
"{{ field.name }}"
  Task       : {{ field.description }}
  Word limit : {{ field.min_words }}–{{ field.max_words }} words
  {% if field.required %}⚠ Required{% else %}Optional{% endif %}

{% endfor %}

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
GUIDELINES
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

Tone: {{ section.prompt_hints.tone }}

Avoid:
{% for item in section.prompt_hints.avoid %}
  - {{ item }}
{% endfor %}

Prefer:
{% for item in section.prompt_hints.prefer %}
  - {{ item }}
{% endfor %}

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
OUTPUT FORMAT
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

Return a single valid JSON object.
No backticks. No explanation. No extra keys.
Start your response with { and end with }

{% endblock %}
